original_title: Best of Carrington-Brown live in Vienna
overview: Carrington-Brown is a multi-lingual, multi-award-winning music and comedy duo that was formed in the UK in 2007. Combining British humor and virtuosic musical talents, this unique pair creates an elegant and brilliant mix of music & comedy.
tagline: Hilariously elegant combination of music and comedy: Carrington-Brown
title: Best of Carrington-Brown live in Vienna
